# The Pantone PMS Color Variety Collection

## Match plastics to your print and packaging colors

Sku#: 2022-044

$ 1,082.00

Add To Cart

Looking for a variety of new PMS colors in plastic? Get the colors you need all in one set. Our new plastic supplement is perfect for adding more colors to the Pantone Plastic Standard Collection or as a stand-alone with sought-after reds, blues, greens, purples, and neutrals.

These plastic chips match our graphics (PMS) color system so that you can match plastics to your print & packaging colors. Each Pantone Plastic Chip provides a physical standard that can be utilized throughout the entire design process.

For more information on The Pantone PMS Color Variety Collection, please email [pantoneorders@pantone.com](mailto:pantoneorders@pantone.com?subject=Enquiry%20Regarding%20The%20Pantone%20PMS%20Color%20Variety%20Collection).

